Important notes:
1. Default installation folder is &quot;C:Program Filesfoobar2000&quot;
2. Front art should be called &quot;*folder*.*&quot; and back art should be called &quot;*back*.*&quot;. You can also add &quot;%artist%.*&quot;
  Those files must be placed with album, e.g. in:
----------------------------
D:MusicMETALLICAReload
-TRACK1.mp3
-TRACK2.mp3
-...
-TRACK13.mp3
-folder.jpg
-back.jpg
-%artist%.jpg
-----------------------------
3. If someone have win 2000, try to install GDI+ http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?familyid=6A63AB9C-DF12-4D41-933C-BE590FEAA05A&amp;displaylang=en
4. Install VC8 SP1 Runtimes. You can find it here: http://acropolis.lokalen.org/2006/10/foobar2000/my-foobar2000-components
5. You need Pentium 3+ or compatible computer, because some plugins use SSE instructions

